title: Jung
subTitle: Desperate to save his son's life, Veer, an honest cop, is faced with an impossible choice when he discovers that the only person who can help him is a notorious criminal behind bars.

title: Swarnakamalam
subTitle: Meenakshi, a young classical dancer who was born in a family of artists, is bitter about the lack of opportunity in India. However, Chandrashekhar changes her outlook and helps her grow.

title: Insaniyat Ke Devta
subTitle: Two friends, Balbir and Anwar, join forces to defeat an influential tycoon who wishes to destroy an ashram and use the property to further his own selfish purposes.

title: Fillers
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of promotional videos and trailers of Bollywood movies featuring popular actors and actresses.

title: Velaiilla Pattadhari

title: Rahul
subTitle: Caught in the emotional crossfire between his divorced parents, an innocent 5-year-old becomes collateral damage, and inevitably, this takes a toll on his health.

title: Ek Vivah Aisa Bhi
subTitle: A tragedy compels Chandni to put off her marriage and singing career. As she takes on new responsibilities, Prem holds their love in his heart for years, and waits for the day when she can come back to him.

title: Naseeb Apna Apna
subTitle: A naive village girl marries the son of a domineering man. However, upon her arrival at his house in the city, she finds out that he is already married.

title: Mard

title: Toofan
subTitle: Separated at birth, the paths of Shyam, a lousy magician unwittingly roped into a crime, and Toofan, a defender of the people, cross again years later as they reunite to avenge their father.

title: Arpan

title: Adharm
subTitle: Mr Verma's decision to disown his son Jaggan sparks a vow of retribution. Years later, Jaggan devises a plan to destroy his family and retaliate against his father.

title: Shivam
